{"type":"message","id":"cf180f88","parentId":"6ccc2fee","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:40:50.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了配置文件！在 `agents.list[0].tools` 里已经有 `allow` 列表，但没有明确排除 `apply_patch`。问题是 `profile: \"coding\"` 默认包含 `group:fs`，而 `group:fs` 包含 `apply_patch`。\n\n解决方案是在 `tools.deny` 里加上 `\"apply_patch\"`。\n\n让我修改配置文件，在 `agents.list[0].tools.deny` 数组中添加 `\"apply_patch\"`。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！在你的 `agents.list[0].tools` 配置里，`profile: \"coding\"` 默认包含了 `apply_patch`，但当前模型不支持它。\n\n我来帮你修复，在 `deny` 列表里加上 `apply_patch`：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ea0fd7603424af8b70200d0","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","oldText":"        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"coding\",\n          \"allow\": [\n            \"browser\",\n            \"read\",\n            \"write\",\n            \"edit\",\n            \"exec\",\n            \"process\",\n            \"sessions_list\",\n            \"sessions_history\",\n            \"sessions_send\",\n            \"sessions_spawn\",\n            \"session_status\",\n            \"subagents\",\n            \"image\",\n            \"canvas\",\n            \"memory_search\",\n            \"memory_get\",\n            \"web_fetch\",\n            \"message\"\n          ],\n          \"deny\": [\n            \"nodes.camera.snap\",\n            \"nodes.screen.record\",\n            \"bash\",\n            \"nodes.camera.stream\",\n            \"nodes.mic.record\",\n            \"nodes.speaker.play\"\n          ]\n        }","newText":"        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"coding\",\n          \"allow\": [\n            \"browser\",\n            \"read\",\n            \"write\",\n            \"edit\",\n            \"exec\",\n            \"process\",\n            \"sessions_list\",\n            \"sessions_history\",\n            \"sessions_send\",\n            \"sessions_spawn\",\n         