{"type":"message","id":"9b2ae8e9","parentId":"e9f1dd39","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:51:04.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求创建一个系统维护员 agent，负责：\n1. 维护 OpenClaw 系统\n2. 学习 openclaw.json 配置\n3. 每天定时查看 warning/error/fatal 日志\n4. 生成报告\n5. 生成维护 openclaw.json 的笔记\n\n这需要：\n1. 在 openclaw.json 中添加一个新的 agent 配置\n2. 配置 cron 定时任务来运行日志检查\n3. 创建相关工作区文件和记忆结构\n\n让我先规划一下需要做什么：\n1. 在 agents.list 中添加一个新的维护员 agent\n2. 配置 cron 任务每天运行\n3. 创建工作区目录和必要的文件\n4. 可能需要配置日志访问\n\n我需要编辑 openclaw.json 来添加这个新 agent。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你创建一个系统维护员 agent，负责 OpenClaw 的日常维护和日志监控。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5e781beaec294389857da283","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","oldText":"    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"default\": true,\n        \"name\": \"CEO Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n          \"fallbacks\": [\n            \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n            \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\"\n          ]\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"CEO\",\n          \"theme\": \"executive leader\",\n          \"emoji\": \"👔\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatar/CEO.png\"\n        },\n        \"groupChat\": {\n          \"mentionPatterns\": [\n            \"@openclaw\",\n            \"@助手\"\n          ]\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"*\"\n          ]\n        },\n        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"coding\",\n          \"allow\": [\n            \"browser\",\n            \"read\",\n            \"write\",\n            \"edit\",\n            \"exec\",\n            \"process\",\n            \"sessions_list\",\n            \"sessions_history\",\n            \"sessions_send\",\n            \"sessions_spawn\",\n            \"session_status\