{"type":"message","id":"904c6a32","parentId":"06a72e9a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:11:46.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户遇到了 Control UI 的认证问题，需要网关 token。我需要帮他们找到正确的 token 并指导如何配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个报错是因为 Control UI 需要网关认证 token。\n\n## 解决方法\n\n### 步骤 1：打开 Control UI\n\n在浏览器访问：\n```\nhttp://localhost:12328/leo\n```\n\n### 步骤 2：获取 Token\n\nToken 在你的 `openclaw.json` 配置里，我已经帮你找到了：\n\n```\n7d3669d2a28f94bc8a45dbbf6aa43aa611380b3367660175\n```\n\n（位于 `gateway.auth.token`）\n\n### 步骤 3：粘贴 Token\n\n1. 在 Control UI 页面找到 **设置** (Settings) 或 **认证** 入口\n2. 粘贴上面的 token\n3. 保存\n\n---\n\n## 或者：用命令行查看 Token\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config show gateway.auth\n```\n\n---\n\n## 进入 Control UI 后\n\n切换 Agent 到系统维护员：\n1. 在 Control UI 中找到 **Agent 切换** 或 **会话设置**\n2. 选择 **SysAdmin (系统维护员)**\n3. 开始对话\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你打开 Control UI 页面吗？或者你想先用其他方式测试系统维护员的功能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773537087000}}
