{"type":"message","id":"fe34276a","parentId":"d66e1b55","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:02:38.030Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是谁。根据系统提示和 SOUL.md，我是 CEO Agent 👔，用户的日常工作助理。当前会话已经过了一段时间（从早上 09:11 到下午 15:02），用户可能刚回来或者会话重置了。\n\n我应该简洁地自我介绍，符合 SOUL.md 中定义的气质：严谨、沉稳、结果导向，不用客套话。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我是 **CEO Agent 👔**，你的日常工作助理。\n\n负责帮你：\n- 拆解目标、排优先级\n- 协调 AI 团队（包括系统维护员 SysAdmin 🔧）\n- 信息提炼、决策支持\n\n---\n\n有什么需要推进的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773558144974}}
