{"type":"message","id":"c5eccc18","parentId":"7cace04b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:46:39.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！sysadmin agent 的配置被简化了，只有基本的 id、name、workspace 和 agentDir，缺少了 model、identity、tools 等关键配置。而且 webchat 默认绑定到 default agent（main），所以 webui 上看不到 sysadmin 选项。\n\n让我查一下 OpenClaw 文档，看看 webui 如何切换 agent，以及如何配置 bindings。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！你的 `sysadmin` agent 配置不完整，而且 **webchat 默认只绑定到 default agent（main）**。\n\n让我查一下如何配置 webui 的 agent 切换：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_590059f63c8945139431e553","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"在 F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs 目录下搜索关于 webui、control-ui、webchat、agent 切换、bindings 配置的文档。找出如何在 web 界面切换 agent 的方法。","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773560794204}}
