{"type":"message","id":"af41d9ff","parentId":"9c81ae76","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:47:52.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"webchat 没有单独的文档。让我查一下 Control UI 的聊天是如何绑定到 agent 的。可能需要在 openclaw.json 中添加 bindings 配置，让 webchat 可以路由到不同的 agent。\n\n根据之前读的 multi-agent 文档，bindings 的匹配顺序是：\n1. peer match\n2. parentPeer match\n3. guildId + roles\n4. guildId\n5. teamId\n6. accountId match\n7. channel-level match (accountId: \"*\")\n8. fallback to default agent\n\n对于 webchat，没有 accountId 的概念，所以可能需要用 peer 或者 channel-level 绑定。\n\n但问题是 Control UI 是一个单一的 WebSocket 连接，它如何知道要发送到哪个 agent？\n\n让我想想... 可能的方法是：\n1. 在 Control UI 中有 agent 选择器，选择后改变 sessionKey 的前缀\n2. 或者在 chat.send 命令中指定 agentId 参数\n3. 或者配置多个 webchat 渠道实例\n\n让我继续搜索文档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6befe08c2bf347608d8a0e2d","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"run","data":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\" -Recurse -Filter \"*.md\" | Select-String -Pattern \"webchat|control.*ui.*agent|chat\\.send.*agent\" -Context 2 | Select-Object -First 30","timeout":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773560860399}}
