{"type":"message","id":"54c3d6f3","parentId":"cb354729","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:48:04.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我先给用户一个初步的解答，基于我已经了解的信息。\n\n根据我读的文档：\n1. Control UI 通过 WebSocket 连接到 Gateway\n2. 会话是通过 sessionKey 来区分的，格式是 `agent:<agentId>:<mainKey>`\n3. bindings 用于路由 inbound 消息到不同的 agent\n\n问题是 Control UI 的聊天界面默认绑定到 default agent（main）。要切换到 sysadmin，可能需要：\n1. 在 Control UI 中有 agent 选择器（如果 UI 支持）\n2. 或者通过配置 bindings 让 webchat 支持多 agent\n3. 或者直接在对话中用命令切换\n\n让我先给用户一个可行的解决方案，同时等子代理的搜索结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据我查阅的文档，**Control UI 目前默认绑定到 default agent（main）**，没有内置的 agent 切换器。但你可以通过以下几种方式实现切换：\n\n## 方案一：配置 webchat bindings（推荐）\n\n在 `openclaw.json` 中添加 `bindings`，让 webchat 可以路由到不同 agent：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7933ba021e04a3581a5da20","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":50,"offset":1}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773560878507}}
