{"type":"message","id":"86211afa","parentId":"33afa201","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:48:34.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置里没有 bindings 部分。我需要添加 bindings 来让 webchat 支持多 agent 切换。\n\n根据文档，bindings 的格式是：\n```json5\n{\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { agentId: \"main\", match: { channel: \"webchat\" } },\n    { agentId: \"sysadmin\", match: { channel: \"webchat\", peer: { kind: \"direct\", id: \"...\" } } }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n但问题是 webchat 的 peer 是什么？Control UI 的聊天可能不支持 peer 区分。\n\n让我想想另一种方案：在 Control UI 中，会话是通过 sessionKey 来区分的。sessionKey 的格式是 `agent:<agentId>:<mainKey>`。如果用户能在 UI 中指定 sessionKey，就能切换到不同的 agent。\n\n但 Control UI 可能没有这个功能。让我给用户一个实用的解决方案。\n\n实际上，最简单的方案可能是：\n1. 添加 bindings 配置，让 webchat 默认路由到 main\n2. 用命令行或 API 创建 sysadmin 会话\n3. 在 Control UI 中通过某种方式切换到那个会话\n\n或者，我可以用 sessions_send 来转发消息到 sysadmin，作为一个临时的解决方案。\n\n让我先给用户解释现状，然后提供一个可行的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前配置没有 `bindings` 部分。让我帮你添加，并解释 Control UI 切换 agent 的方法：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1cc21a34d82242bb92068a1d","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","oldText":"  \"plugins\": {","newText":"  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"match\": { \"channel\": \"webchat\" }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"plugins\": {"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773560890323}}
