{"type":"message","id":"287ff544","parentId":"da74d47a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T07:52:16.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"sysadmin 的配置里已经有 `apply_patch` 在 deny 列表中了。但警告还是出现了，可能是因为配置还没有重新加载。\n\n让我检查一下配置是否正确，然后告诉用户如何重启 Gateway 让配置生效。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`sysadmin` 的配置里已经有 `apply_patch` 在 deny 列表中了。警告是因为 Gateway 还没有重新加载配置。\n\n## 重启 Gateway 让配置生效\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者如果 Gateway 是作为服务运行的：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway stop\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n## 系统维护员已就绪！✅\n\n**sysadmin agent 配置摘要：**\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **ID** | `sysadmin` |\n| **名称** | 系统维护员 🔧 |\n| **工作区** | `~/.openclaw/workspace-sysadmin` |\n| **模型** | `dashscope/qwen-turbo` |\n| **心跳** | 每 24 小时自动巡检 |\n| **工具策略** | `coding` profile，deny `apply_patch` |\n\n---\n\n## 与 sysadmin 对话\n\n```bash\n# 直接对话\nopenclaw agent --agent sysadmin --message \"检查今天的 error 日志\"\n\n# 交互式对话\nopenclaw tui --session agent:sysadmin:main\n\n# 发送到 WhatsApp\nopenclaw agent --agent sysadmin --message \"生成维护报告\" --deliver --reply-channel whatsapp --reply-to \"+8618186144326\"\n```\n\n---\n\n**重启 Gateway 后，警告就会消失。需要我帮你执行重启吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773561130805}}
